<%= render Content::CampaignHeroComponent.new(
  title: ["Get Into Teaching", "events"],
  colour: "yellow",
  image: "static/images/content/hero-images/0025.jpg"
) %>

<div class="row inset">
  <section class="col col-720 statement">
    <h2 class="pink xlarge bold">What to expect</h2>
  </section>

  <section class="col col-720">
    <p>We understand everyoneâ€™s journey into the classroom is different. But whether you're ready to start your career in teaching, or just curious, we can answer your queries at a Get Into Teaching event.</p>

    <p>These relaxed and informative events provide a one-stop shop of information and support. They'll give you the opportunity to get expert advice and talk to teachers and local training providers.</p>

  </section>

  <section class="col col-720">
    <h3 class="heading-m">At our Get Into Teaching events</h3>
    
    <p>You can drop in at any time during an event to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>chat to teachers and find out what life as a teacher is really like</li>
      <li>understand what qualifications you need and the different ways to train</li>
      <li>talk to training providers about the courses they offer</li>
      <li>learn what funding is available</li>
      <li>get tips from expert advisers on how to apply for teacher training</li>
      <li>meet people like you who are thinking about becoming a teacher</li>
    </ul>

<p>Watch our video to find out how what happens at a Get Into Teaching event.</p>

    <div class="video">
      <%= render Content::YoutubeVideoComponent.new(
        id: "w3AVk-ByUaA",
        title: "A video about what happens at a Get Into Teaching event"
      ) %>
      <p><a href="/events/what-happens-at-events-transcript">Read the transcript for the 'What happens at a Get Into Teaching event' video</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="col col-720">
    <h3 class="heading-m">Reserve your place</h3>
    <p>You'll need to register to attend a Get Into Teaching event. Places are limited, so the sooner you sign up, the better.</p>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="grey">
    <section class="col col-full-content inset">
      <%= render TextBlockWithOneImageComponent.new(
        heading: "Events in your region",
        colour: "blue",
        image_path: "static/images/content/homepage/here-to-help.jpg",
        image_alt: "A woman at a Get Into Teaching event wearing a blue T-shirt with Here to Help written on it.",
      ) %>

      <% if @git_events.any? %>
        <section id="events" class="category__cards">
          <%= tag.nav(class: "category__nav-cards") do %>
            <ul class="one-column horizontal">
              <%= render(Events::CardComponent.with_collection(categorise_events(@git_events, params))) %>
            </ul>
          <% end %>
          <div>
            <h3 class="heading-s">Can't find what you're looking for?</h3>
            <p>You can also take a look at <%= link_to("teacher training provider events", events_path({ teaching_events_search: { type: ["provider"] }}), class: "link--black") %> in your area.</p>
          </div>
        </section>
      <% else %>
        <section class="col col-720 col-space-m">
          <p><strong>We do not have any Get Into Teaching events open for registration right now. We'll update this page with new Get Into Teaching events soon.</strong></p>
        </section>

        <section class="col col-720">
          <p>In the meantime, take a look at <%= link_to("teacher training provider events", events_path({ teaching_events_search: { type: ["provider"] }}), class: "link--black") %> in your area or online.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="col col-720">
          <h2 class="heading-m">Get event updates and advice in your inbox</h2>

          <p>Get a better idea if teaching is right for you with regular information on:</p>

          <ul>
            <li>what it's like to be a teacher</li>
            <li>different ways to train</li>
            <li>events near you</li>
          </ul>

          <p><%= link_to("Get event updates and advice in your inbox", mailing_list_steps_path, class: "link--black") %>.</p>
        </section>
      <% end %>
    </section>
  </div>

  <section class="col col-full-page what-theyre-saying">
    <div class="triangle on-grey yellow-triangle">
      <svg height="100%" width="100%" viewBox="0 0 100 100" preserveAspectRatio="none">
        <polygon points="0,100 100,0 100,100"></polygon>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="subheading">
      <h2 class="heading--box-pink heading-xl heading--margin-0">What they're saying</h2>
    </div>
    <figure>
      <blockquote>Really helpful and friendly. Provided very tangible advice on next steps.</blockquote>
    </figure>
  </section>
</div>
